            <title>[CASSANDRA-14372] data_file_directories config - update documentation in cassandra.yaml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-14372</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If &quot;data_file_directories&quot; configuration is enabled with multiple directories, data is partitioned by token range so that data gets distributed evenly. But the current documentation says that &quot;Cassandra will spread data evenly across them, subject to the granularity of the configured compaction strategy&quot;. Need to update this comment to reflect the correct behavior.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
